Dear PharmaTech Quality Assurance Team,

I am writing to formally report a product quality complaint regarding Metformin Hydrochloride Tablets 500mg received by City General Hospital Pharmacy.

COMPLAINT DETAILS:
- Product Name: Metformin Hydrochloride Tablets
- Product Strength: 500mg
- Batch/Lot Number: ABC-2024-0891
- Manufacturing Date: 15-August-2023
- Expiry Date: 14-August-2026
- Quantity Affected: 250 kg (approximately 500,000 tablets)

ISSUE DESCRIPTION:
Upon visual inspection during routine incoming goods check, our pharmacy staff identified significant discoloration in multiple bottles from the above batch. Approximately 15% of tablets show a yellowish-brown discoloration inconsistent with the standard white appearance. Two patients have reported unusual taste when taking medication from this batch. No adverse events have been confirmed, but we have quarantined the remaining stock.

We request immediate investigation and a formal response within 48 hours as per our supply agreement.

Complaint Type: Product Quality / Discoloration
